Start server command:

python -m SimpleHTTPServer 8000


Note:

Call the files indicating the Application Server address.

No caso o Server em Python (SimpleHTTPServer)
- - -> So the requests will come with the Headers: OPTIONS. <- - -

If you just open a file and run it, it won't happen.


--- EXAMPLES --- 
Right:	http://localhost:8000/get-categories.html
Wrong:	file:///home/adailsilva/Apps/SimpleHTTPServer/get-categories.html
